(40, 9, 35, 40, 4, 23, 24, 'preaching the gospel of the kingdom', 'Healing and Teaching Ministry', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus'' ministry of teaching and healing. They describe his activities in synagogues and his role in addressing various sicknesses and diseases among the people.', 'theme', 0.398, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
